-- Emirates Islamic Offers 100% Financing for U.A.E. Homes
-- B y   E d i t o r s :   C h r i s t o p h e r   S c i n t a
-- 2012-04-14T11:39:21Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-14/emirates-islamic-offers-100-financing-for-u-a-e-homes.html
Emirates Islamic Bank ({EIB)  is offering
 United Arab Emirates ’ citizens full home financing through new
Shariah-compliant mortgages with rates starting at 4.99 percent,
it said in an e-mailed statement today.  Bina’a, meaning ‘to build’ in Arabic, is the only product
in the country that offers 100 percent financing, the state-
controlled lender said. Customers can finance an existing or
new-build property and can fix their rate and installments for
as many as five years, it added. 